# Pre-edit hashes from review/fix sessions
/tmp/*-pre-edit-hashes.txt

# TeamLead-plugin self-dogfood state (generated by /teamwork-leader on plugin source repo)
# These files orchestrate a TeamLead charter and should not be in the plugin distribution.
# Downstream projects using /teamwork-leader generate the same files in their own project root —
# they decide whether to gitignore them in their own .gitignore.
PROGRESS.md
tasks.md
docs/audit-trail.jsonl
docs/pre-task-estimates.jsonl
docs/PROGRESS.teamlead*.md
docs/tasks.teamlead*.md
